data.description: Cozy 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Joplin, MO where you'll be greeted by the warmth of oak cabinets in the kitchen with appliances included. Outside, you'll find a detached one-car garage for your convenience, along with a fully fenced backyard offering privacy and security. Relax and unwind on the covered porch at both the front and back of the home, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or hosting gatherings with friends and family. Additionally, this home features an unfinished basement, allowing you the opportunity to customize and create your ideal space. Don't miss the chance to make this lovely property your own and experience the comforts it has to offer.
